flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Read Resume<br/>Directory"]
    B --> C[List Resume Files]
    C --> D[CALL PARALLEL<br/>Evaluate Resumes]
    subgraph Parallel Evaluation
    D --> E1["Load Resume 1"]
    D --> E2["Load Resume 2"]
    D --> EN["Load Resume N"]
    E1 --> F1["LLM Judge:<br/>Score & Criteria Check"]
    E2 --> F2["LLM Judge:<br/>Score & Criteria Check"]
    EN --> FN["LLM Judge:<br/>Score & Criteria Check"]
    end
    F1 --> G[Collect Results]
    F2 --> G
    FN --> G
    G --> H{All Resumes<br/>Evaluated?}
    H -->|No| D
    H -->|Yes| I["Aggregate Scores"]
    I --> J["Rank Candidates"]
    J --> K{Meets Qualification<br/>Threshold?}
    K -->|Yes| L["Add to<br/>Qualified List"]
    K -->|No| M["Add to<br/>Rejected List"]
    L --> N[Merge Lists]
    M --> N
    N --> O["Generate<br/>Summary Report"]
    O --> P([End])